---
import DisplayHeading from '../ui/DisplayHeading.astro';
import GradientText from '../ui/GradientText.astro';
import SectionEyebrow from '../ui/SectionEyebrow.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="pt-14 md:pt-20 pb-8 md:pb-10 relative">
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full opacity-20 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--brand-orange) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(30%, -30%);"
  ></div>
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 rounded-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--brand-red) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-30%, 30%);"
  ></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-brand-gradient"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
    <div>
      <SectionEyebrow>About the Tour</SectionEyebrow>
      <DisplayHeading class="text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05] mb-8">
        Where technology<br />
        meets <GradientText>culture</GradientText>.
      </DisplayHeading>

      <div class="relative pl-8 mb-8">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-2 bottom-2 w-1 rounded-full border-brand-gradient-v"></div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-[17px]">
          <span class="drop-cap drop-cap--md float-left mr-3 mt-1 leading-none">T</span>
          he Seoul Tech &amp; Culture Tour 2026 was organized by the Department of Computer Science
          during 18&ndash;21 May 2026, offering students a rare opportunity to engage directly with
          South Korea's world-leading universities and Seoul's smart-city innovation centers.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
          Led by Prof. Howard Leung and Dr. Kenneth Lee, 25 undergraduate students visited
          Sungkyunkwan University (SKKU), the KAIST AI Hub and CVML Lab, Korea University, Yonsei
          University's Engineering Research Park, and the Seoul TOPIS smart-transportation control
          center at Seoul City Hall.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
          Beyond the tech circuit, students experienced Seoul firsthand &mdash; from the Hongdae
          and Shinchon-Ewha districts where they stayed to the Seoul Gallery at City Hall &mdash;
          bridging Korea's modern identity with its everyday culture.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-5 grid-rows-2 gap-3 h-[460px]">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1709382204074-de328e811d1c?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3Nzg4Nzd8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwyfHx1bml2ZXJzaXR5JTIwc3R1ZGVudHMlMjBjYW1wdXMlMjBLb3JlYSUyMHRlY2hub2xvZ3l8ZW58MXx8fHwxNzc5MzY4MzA4fDA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=800"
        alt="Students on campus"
        class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full h-full col-span-3 row-span-2 shadow-md"
      />
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1637073759412-9d3ddd764bd8?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3Nzg4Nzd8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwyfHxTZW91bCUyMGNpdHlzY2FwZSUyMG5pZ2h0JTIwbW9kZXJufGVufDF8fHx8MTc3OTM2ODMwOHww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=600"
        alt="Seoul bridge at night"
        class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full h-full col-span-2 row-span-1 shadow-md"
      />
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1777551105702-c45e42dd945d?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3Nzg4Nzd8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwyfHxTZW91bCUyMEd5ZW9uZ2Jva2d1bmclMjBwYWxhY2UlMjBtb2Rlcm4lMjBza3lsaW5lfGVufDF8fHx8MTc3OTM2ODMxM3ww&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=600"
        alt="Seoul skyline at dusk"
        class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full h-full col-span-2 row-span-1 shadow-md"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
